**Runner** | Townsfolk Miscellaneous
__Basics__
Once per game, if attacked by a werewolf, the Runner shall escape.
__Details__
When they are attacked, the Runner will not die, but will be vulnerable to future attacks. 
If a Runner is targeted by any kill other than a werewolf kill, they will die the first time. 
Runners are informed that they were attacked. If a Runner evades the wolfpack, the wolfpack is told why.
